{"tid":1907041,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"武漢肺炎澳洲首現人傳人感染 雪梨一日兩起","createTime":"2020-03-02T10:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T12:27:12.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad6b49f1936ac755727a6c9be68af9b48e242a8","tid":1907041,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"2019年冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，新冠肺炎）疫情持續在全球擴散，澳洲今天首次傳出人傳人感染個案，雪梨一日有兩起。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司（ABC）報導，新南威爾斯州首府雪梨傳出兩起人傳人感染個案。其中一名感染者，是來自雪梨西區、現年53歲的醫護人員，他最近3個月未曾出國旅行，尚未查出他是如何感染。<br />\n<br />\n另一感染個案，是現年41歲女性，她的43歲哥哥，稍早從伊朗返回澳洲，隨後在29日被確診。報導提到，她近期並未前往伊朗，但與哥哥曾有近距離接觸。<br />\n<br />\n新南威爾斯州衛生局長哈札德（Brad Hazzard）表示，當地連續傳出兩起人傳人個案，情況「特別引人關注」。<br />\n<br />\n哈札德建議，民眾應該停止與人握手，在與人親吻時，更要先了解存在的風險。<br />\n<br />\n新南威爾斯州首席醫官項特（Kerry Chant）指出，有醫護人員受感染的消息，反映出可能有其他受感染案例並未被察覺到。<br />\n<br />\n新南威爾斯州目前共有9名確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n西澳州首府伯斯1日傳出澳洲首起新冠肺炎患者死亡個案。死者為78歲男子，稍早於鑽石公主號郵輪接受隔離，但在返回澳洲後病發身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4383545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120944%2F4383545&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=21a0f7fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4383545</a>"},{"pid":"0367ac4613921641cbc0bc9ee4006d2a67f556d9","tid":1907041,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66787e8c9b4ffb6b8fa4bdbb75e1128f956015d","tid":1907041,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"兩宗就兩宗<br />\n<br />\n起乜撚嘢？"},{"pid":"be97b6b6915ae9f5a9fe55deee327cc4e86ab844","tid":1907041,"uid":31237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b66787e8c9b4ffb6b8fa4bdbb75e1128f956015d","tid":1907041,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"兩宗就兩宗<br />\n<br />\n起乜撚嘢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"一起謀殺案"},{"pid":"2279e00af202140cbf982faf63e4ed9a8be4eeea","tid":1907041,"uid":66433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"澳洲太遲封伊朗"},{"pid":"f2e23dabc7f37793bed1c126c3e5952661806704","tid":1907041,"uid":3647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"起你老母"},{"pid":"8ee9927234c522c7a9c30e37ad7d709313ec3c41","tid":1907041,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e5085ae6db12c81dfdc4b291603ded3d39496d","tid":1907041,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"一日兩起，朝早瞓醒晏晝瞓晏覺起多次？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6477caf554cf3cb75be5e28b0ba42aa889c0fb","tid":1907041,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2afd08e5f23b6eb2bd52cda53b974d0c987c6d7","tid":1907041,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:27:12.000Z","msg":"起你老母<br />\n內你老母<br />\n清朝朝你老母<br />\n中央中你老母"}]}